tafsir[9]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"Khadiru wi'ani: Mussaa (yo o his): Min hari mi wi'iino ma: ""pellet, an -Muusaa- a hattantaake muГұal e dow fiyaake ko mi waЙ—ata kon""."
  18,76,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Si mi lanndike fii huunde Й“aawo ngol laawol Й—oo haray seedu e an, haray gomЙ—ii a hewtii e nokku mo ngantu mo accata fii wonndugol e an; sabu lunndagol an yamiroore maaЙ—a laabi tati."
  18,77,"ЖҒe yahi haa Й“e hewti e yimЙ“e saare Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iri yimЙ“e mayre Й“en Гұaametee, yimЙ“e saare nden salii Гұamminngol Й“e, e tottugol e maЙ“Й“e hakkee wernugol, Й“e tawi ka saare maade woГұiindi Й“attii-ndi yanugol yirba, Khadiru wurti ndi haa ndi feewi, Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Khadiru: ""Sinno a yiЙ—ii Жҙittugol njoddi fii moЖҙЖҙintingol ndi a Жҙettayno Й—um; sabu katonnjinal me'en e Й—um Й“aawo salagol maЙ“Й“e wernugol en."
  18,78,"Khadiru maakani Muusaa: ""Ngool falagol Й—oo sabu anngal Жҙettugol njoddi fii wurtugol maadi ndin ko Й—um woni nokku seedigal ngal hakkunde an e ma'a, aray mi humpite firo kon ko a hattananooka munГұaade e dow mun e ko yi'uЙ—aa kon miЙ—o waЙ—a Й—um."
  18,79,"Si ko kan laana ka yeddirЙ—aa mi sabu yulugol ka; hari ka wonanii lo'uЙ“e hiЙ“e gollera ka ka maayo Й“e hattantaake hiwugol ka, mi faalaa ko mi waЙ—i kon e makka yo wontan ka ayyibe; fii wata halor ka lamЙ—o wonЙ—o yeeso maЙ“Й“e on, on jaЙ“toowo kala laana moЖҙЖҙuka e junngo jom makka, o Й—ala kala laana wonnduka e ayiiibe."
  18,80,"Si ko on suka mo yeddirЙ—aa lam sabu warugol mo neene makko e baaba makko laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e, tawi kanko e Ganndal Alla ko o keefeeru, men huli si o hellifaama wata o ukkuЙ“e e yeddugol Alla e bewre sabu fantude giggol maЙ“Й“e e makko, maaЙ—un sabu fantude katojinal maЙ“Й“e e makko."
  18,81,"Men faalaa yo Alla lontinanЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й—o Й“urЙ—o mo moЖҙЖҙude Diina e laaЙ“al immorde e bakkaatu, e Й“urЙ—o Й“adaade yurmeende jibinЙ“e Й“en Й—iЙ—o."
  18,82,"Si ko ndin maadi ndi mi moЖҙЖҙontini Й—um yedduЙ—aa mi e moЖҙЖҙintingol ndi, ko fii cukaloy Й—iЙ—o koy baaba mun maayi no ka saare nde aruЙ—en e mu'un, tawi jawdi no iranaa koy ka ley maadi, baaba koy cukaloy Й—iЙ—oy laatino neЙ—Й—o moЖҙЖҙo, Joomi maaЙ—a faalaa -an Muusaa- yo Й“e mawnu Й“e hewtu duuЙ“i peewal, Й“e yaltina jawdi maЙ“Й“e iraandi ndin ka ley maadi; sinno maadi ndin yanuno jooni jawdi maЙ“Й“e ndin yaltitayno ndi weeЙ“itanoo yeebagol, ndee eЙ“Й“oore Й—oo laatike Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa nde O YurmaaЙ“e, mi waЙ—iraali Й—um immorde e tinnaare am, Й—um ko firo ko a hattanaaka munГұaade e dow mun kon."
  18,83,"SirkooЙ“e Й“en e Alyahuuda en no lanndaade ma -an NulaaЙ—o- e ndarndagol fii kumpital jom gaLlaaЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i, maaku: ""Arma mi janngana on seeЙ—a e kumpital fii makko ko taskoron Й—um waajitoЙ—on""."
